## This plugin enables password change feature for AfterLogic WebMail, so that user can change their email account password from within WebMail account settings area. 
## wiki : http://netwinsite.com/poppassd/
## c: The connection
## user : the username used in the packed
## pass : the old password
## newpass : the new password
##
event poppassd_event%(c: connection,user:string,pass:string,newpass:string%);


